3. Rules and Regulations
General Guidelines for Users

1. Safe Usage
Device Security: Protect your device with a password or biometric lock to prevent unauthorized access to your personal diary.
Backup Habits: Regularly export your entries if they are critical, as local storage can be cleared if the app is uninstalled.
2. Prohibited Actions
Illegal Content: Do not use the app to store or generate content that violates local or international laws.
Malicious Use: Do not attempt to bypass security features or interfere with the app's functionality.
3. Community & Integrity
Daily Dairy is a private tool. Please respect the privacy of others if they share their device with you.
4. Refund & Subscription Policy
(Note: Only applicable if premium features are added in the future)

Free Version: The core features of Daily Dairy are free to use, supported by ads.
Premium Upgrades: Any future one-time purchases or subscriptions will be handled through the official Google Play Store or Apple App Store billing systems. Refunds will be subject to the respective store's refund policy.
Contact Information
For any questions regarding these policies, please reach out through the official support channels within the app settings or via the store listing contact.
